            "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base",
            "heading_tag_column_1": "h3",
            "text_column_1": "<p>The prehnite is cut as a smooth cabochon — no facets, just a glowing drop of green that deepens at the center and lightens at the edges. Each stone is hand-selected for color and clarity. The gold frame is cast using lost-wax technique and hand-finished in our NYC studio.</p><p>These earrings end just below the jawline — visible but delicate. The prehnite drop sways gently with movement. Comfortable for extended wear, light enough you may forget you have them on.</p>",
