            "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base",
            "heading_tag_column_1": "h3",
            "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Pieces:</strong> Put jewelry on last, take it off first. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Store in the provided pouch. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals. Pearls benefit from being worn — natural skin oils maintain their luster.</p>",
